summary.span: 提供返回预定义 实例的静态属性，这些实例对应于 Unicode 规范中的块。

span.span: Provides static properties that return predefined instances that correspond to blocks from the Unicode specification.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 您使用属性来检索的 Unicode 命名区域，其中每个连续块的 Unicode 码位组成。You use properties to retrieve Unicode named ranges, each of which consists of a contiguous block of Unicode code points. 一些范围包括未定义的码位。Some ranges include undefined code points. 例如，在**亚美尼亚语**Unicode 块 (u+0530-U + 058F)，u+0530，U + 0557年-U + 0558，U + 0560，U + 0588，和 U + 058B 058 C 是不确定。For example, in the **Armenian** Unicode block (U+0530-U+058F), U+0530, U+0557-U+0558, U+0560, U+0588, and U+058B-058C are undefined. 一个或多个未定义的码位可以出现在处结束的范围，或任意位置之间的范围的开头。One or more undefined code points can occur at the beginning of a range, at the end of a range, or anywhere in between. 目前，仅命名区域中基本多语言平面 (BMP)，该类用于扩展从 u+0000 到 U + FFFF 类支持。Currently, the class supports only named ranges in the Basic Multilingual Plane (BMP), which extends from U+0000 to U+FFFF.
